@GameGaraj.Order.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5015
@userId = 5b814009-4ed7-4617-803c-56ed0adebdb6

### Weather Forecast (Test)
GET {{GameGaraj.Order.API_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Orders by UserId
GET {{GameGaraj.Order.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Order
POST {{GameGaraj.Order.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buyerId": "{{userId}}",
  "address": {
    "firstName": "Test",
    "lastName": "User",
    "phoneNumber": "+90 555 123 4567",
    "province": "İstanbul",
    "district": "Kadıköy",
    "neighborhood": "Caferağa",
    "postalCode": "34710",
    "addressDetail": "Test Sokak No:1"
  },
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": "test-product-id",
      "productName": "Test Product",
      "pictureUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/150",
      "price": 100.00
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get User Addresses (Delivery)
GET {{GameGaraj.Order.API_HostAddress}}/api/useraddresses?type=Delivery
Accept: application/json

###

### Get User Addresses (Invoice)
GET {{GameGaraj.Order.API_HostAddress}}/api/useraddresses?type=Invoice
Accept: application/json

